      {
        "legenda": "There’s one detail that can change everything when choosing a Golden Visa.\nㅤ\nIt’s not the price.\nIt’s not the country.\nIt’s whether you actually need to live there.\nㅤ\nSome programs require real presence. Others don’t.\n🇵🇹 Portugal → ~7 days per year\n🇮🇹 Italy → no minimum stay\nㅤ\nThat one difference can completely reshape your lifestyle and freedom.\nThe real question is: what fits your plan?\nㅤ\n#GoldenVisa #Portugal #Italy #InvestmentMigration #EUResidency #MoveAbroad #GlobalCitizenship #WealthStrategy",
        "curtidas": 6,
        "comentarios": 0,
        "tipo": "video"
      },
      {
        "legenda": "Most people compare Golden Visas the wrong way.\nThey focus on price… instead of strategy.\nㅤ\n🇬🇷 Greece looks cheap\n🇲🇹 Malta looks expensive\n🇵🇹 Portugal plays the long game\nㅤ\nBut here’s the truth: they’re built for completely different goals.\nㅤ\nThe right question isn’t “What’s cheaper?”\nIt’s “What fits my strategy?”\nㅤ\nBecause the best Golden Visa isn’t the cheapest one — it’s the one aligned with your future.\nㅤ\n#GoldenVisa #Portugal #Greece #Malta #InvestmentMigration #GlobalCitizenship #MoveAbroad #EUResidency #WealthStrategy",
        "curtidas": 11,
        "comentarios": 0,
        "tipo": "video"
      },
      {
        "legenda": "A record 180,000 Americans moved abroad in 2025 - and the number keeps rising. Lower costs, better healthcare, tax efficiency, and lifestyle are all driving the shift.\nㅤ\nBut the best country for you depends entirely on your profile. A retiree, a remote worker, a family, and a high-net-worth investor each have a different answer. Our 2026 guide covers all 23 destinations in detail - from European favourites like Portugal and Spain to Caribbean citizenship programs and Asia-Pacific options like Singapore and New Zealand.\nㅤ\nWhatever your motivation, there's a smarter way to make the move.\nㅤ\n🔍 Explore the full guide via the link in bio.\nㅤ\n#AmericansAbroad #MoveAbroad #BestCountriesToLiveIn #ExpatLife #GoldenVisa #CitizenshipByInvestment #MoveToPortugal #MoveToSpain #CaribbeanCBI #GlobalMobility #ResidencyByInvestment #TaxOptimization #DigitalNomad #MoveToEurope #SecondPassport #GlobalCitizenSolutions #AmericanExpat #PlanB2026",
